window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Bounty hunter John Smoke gets more than he bargained for when the search for a small-time thug reveals a dragon man.</b></p> <p>Bailed out by a mysterious wizard, John Smoke, an ex-con turned bounty hunter, is returned to his home with his life hanging by a thread. Aided by his sharpshooting wife, Sid, they set out on an explosive mission against dragon invaders sent to enslave mankind.</p> <p>Through inter-dimensional portals, savage winged dragon men, ferocious dragons and shapeshifting monstrosities wielding otherworldly magical powers threaten the very existence of humanity. And it will take more than flesh and blood to stop them before they seal the world's fate.</p> <p>No matter what the cost, Smoke, Sid, and a formidable group of allies from other worlds must unearth ancient powers long buried—or see the life they know come to an explosive end.</p> <p><b>If you are a fan of </b><b><i>The Dresden Files, The Blacklist, Supernatural, The X-Files</i></b><b>, and all things wild and dragon crazy, then grab this book now before the bad guys take it away!</b></p> <p>Publisher note: This standalone series ties in to The Supernatural Bounty Hunter Files and The Henchmen Chronicles series.</p> <p>This Edition includes the following books:</p> <p>Smoke and Fire—Book 1</p> <p>Smoke Screen—Book 2</p> <p>Smoke Stack—Book 3</p> <p>Smoke Break—Book 4</p> <p>Smoke Ring—Book 5</p> <p>Smoke Release—Book 6</p> <p>Dragon Smoke—Book 7</p> <p>Rising Smoke—Book 8</p>"; 
